review: had such a fun experience for my nieces birthday. we will definitely be back. thank you!

room_title: Escape room "Project Sabotage" by Puzzle Plex in Wichita
review: Our group had a blast! Wonderful staff and management. The three rooms we did: Boring Life, Project 403, And Sabotage were exceptional with the last two as standouts. Can't recommend highly enough!

room_title: Escape room "Project Sabotage" by Puzzle Plex in Wichita
review: What an amazing experience we had. We had to split in two teams and play sabotages against each other. It was a race down to the wire where our team won with only one second to spare. I thought the clues were just enough to spread our time out and thoroughly enjoy our full hour.
